# <type>: <subject> (max 50 chars)

# <body> (optional, wrap at 72 chars)

# <footer> (optional)

# Type can be:
#   feat     : new feature
#   fix      : bug fix  
#   docs     : documentation only
#   style    : formatting, missing semicolons, etc (no code change)
#   refactor : code change that neither fixes a bug nor adds a feature
#   perf     : code change that improves performance
#   test     : adding missing tests
#   chore    : maintain (updating grunt tasks etc, no code change)
#   build    : changes to build process
#   ci       : changes to CI configuration

# Example:
# feat: add customer order tracking API
#
# - Implement REST endpoints for order status
# - Add database migrations for order history
# - Include comprehensive test coverage
#
